    <!--
      High-stack core zone, lightweight replacement.
      This grouped model preserves the six infield stack_core_s* footprints with
      primitive boxes and removes the isolated outer stack instance so startup
      no longer loads any container-multi-stack meshes in this scene.

      Visual refresh: keep primitive stack boxes and reuse a small set of
      weathered container skins so the high-stack area reads as cargo stacks
      without bringing back the original multi-stack mesh instances.
